    • equals

      public final boolean equals(Object o) throws ReadDeniedException, AuthenticationRequiredException
      An RDFNode is equal to another enhanced node n iff the underlying nodes are equal. We generalise to allow the other object to be any class implementing asNode, because we allow other implementations of Resource, at least in principle. This is deemed to be a complete and correct interpretation of RDFNode equality, which is why this method has been marked final.
      Specified by:
      equals in interface SecuredItem
      Overrides:
      equals in class SecuredItemImpl
      Parameters:

      Returns:
      True if o is equal to this node.
      Throws:
      ReadDeniedException
      AuthenticationRequiredException
